invisible-space\" data-verified=\"redactor\" data-redactor-tag=\"span\" data-redactor-class=\"redactor-invisible-space\">&nbsp;on dealing with the expectations of others:<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;You have no responsibility to live up to what other people think you ought to accomplish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>I have no responsibility to be like they expect me to be. It&#8217;s their mistake, not my failing.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">Source:&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/0393355624\/ref=as_li_qf_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;tag=jamesclearema-20&amp;creative=9325&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;creativeASIN=0393355624&amp;linkId=002e09b368f270e1442a7766dcb6dc4e\">Surely You&#8217;re Joking, Mr. Feynman!<\/a><span class=\"redactor-invisible-space\" data-verified=\"redactor\" data-redactor-tag=\"span\" data-redactor-class=\"redactor-invisible-space\"><br><\/span><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Whose expectations am I trying to fulfill? My own or those of someone else?<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Until next week,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>James Clear<br><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">Author of the million-copy bestseller,&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\/\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https:\/\/atomichabits.com\">Atomic Habits<\/a><br><\/em><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">Creator of&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/habitsacademy.com\/\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https:\/\/habitsacademy.com\/\">The Habits Academy<\/a>&nbsp;and the&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.vercel.app\/habit-journal\" data-cke-saved-href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.vercel.app\/habit-journal\">Habit Journal<\/a><\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>P.S.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/jamesclear.vercel.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/bilingual.png\">&#8220;Wow, you&#8217;re bilingual?!&#8221;<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>P.P.S. Thanks to&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/MrGrokNRoll\/status\/1226762342513467392\">Jens Reineking<\/a>&nbsp;for sharing today&#8217;s question with m